
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "MainAward";
}

<html>
<head>
    <style>
        dl, ol, ul {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 0rem;
            padding: 0 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #4B4B4B !important;
        }

        .award_content p {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            color: #4B4B4B !important;
        }

        .award_content {
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #4B4B4B !important;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #223871;
        }

        @@media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }

            .award_content p {
                font-weight: 600;
                margin-bottom: 0;
                color: #4B4B4B !important;
                padding-left: 20px;
                color: #223871;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section style="padding: 0px 0;">
        <div class="main_div">
            <div class="main_banner">
                <img src="~/Images/award/award_banner.png" width="100%">
            </div>
            <div class="full_content my-5">
                <div class="award_content">
                    <div class="pageheading">
                        <h1>Award</h1>
                    </div>
                    <img src="~/Images/award/award_sub_banner.png" width="100%" class="aard_img">
                </div>
                <h1 class="mt-5">Apple Distinguished Schools recognition</h1>
                <div class="row mt-4">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <img src="~/Images/award/cr_1.png" width="100%">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <img src="~/Images/award/cr_2.png" width="100%">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <img src="~/Images/award/cr_3.png" width="100%">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="award_content">
                    <p>1. Introduction Section:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Heading: “What is an Apple Distinguished School?”</li>
                        <li>
                            Content: A brief explanation of the Apple Distinguished School program, what it recognizes (innovation, leadership, and educational excellence), and why it’s
                            important in the context of 21st-century learning.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Achievement Announcement Section:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Heading:</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>“MLSI’s Journey to Becoming an Apple Distinguished School”</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Content</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        Detailed content about how Apple technology is integrated into MLSI’s learning environments. Discuss the impact on students’ learning experiences,
                        collaborative projects, creative expression, and problem-solving.
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Add Bullet Points or Highlights:</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>4. Recognition Section:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Heading:</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>“What It Means to Be an Apple Distinguished School”</p>

                    <ul>
                        <li>Content:</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        Discuss the benefits of being an Apple Distinguished School, the ongoing commitment to innovation in education, and what this recognition means for
                        MLSI’s future.
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>CTA:</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>“Discover More About MLSI’s Technology-Driven Programs“</p>

                    <p>5. Future Vision Section:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Heading:</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>“Looking Ahead: Continuing Innovation at MLSI”</p>

                    <ul>
                        <li>Content:</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        A forward-looking statement about how MLSI will continue to lead in educational technology innovation, including future plans, ongoing teacher training,
                        and how the school will evolve its curriculum.
                    </p>

                    <p>6. Conclusion:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Heading:</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>“Join MLSI’s Technological Journey”</p>

                    <ul>
                        <li>Content:</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Invite prospective students and parents to learn more about the school and its forward-thinking approach. Include a CTA like “Explore Admissions” or “Visit Our Campus.”</p>

                    <ul>
                        <li>CTA:</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Buttons for “Explore Admissions” and “Contact Us”</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>